comments: Adebayo (MIA) makes clean contact with the ball and deflects it away from Wembanyama (SAS), any additional contact is deemed incidental.
Wembanyama (SAS) firms over to his left leg in Robinson's (MIA) path and does not deliver illegal contact during the pick.
Vassell (SAS) splits his feet at the start of his dribble.
Johnson (SAS) brings his right hand toward Butler's (MIA) front and marginal contact occurs during Butler's drive.
Adebayo (MIA) firms up to his right leg in Johnson's (SAS) path and absorbs the incidental contact during the pick.
While defending the drive to the basket and shot attempt, Collins (SAS) absorbs the oncoming contact during Butler's (MIA) driving shot attempt and makes marginal contact with his arm.
Jaquez Jr. (MIA) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Johnson (SAS) prior to incidental arm contact occurring during the drive.
After Butler (MIA) gets possession of the loose ball, Johnson extends both hands and initiates contact with Butler's lower body which dislodges him from his position.
Johnson (SAS) avoids making contact with Butler's (MIA) arm as he brings his right hand to the ball during Butler's rip-through.
Johnson (SAS) commits a take foul on Butler (MIA).
Sochan (SAS) briefly brings his left arm toward Jaquez Jr.'s (MIA) front as he crosses half-court.
Sochan (SAS) commits a take foul on Richardson (MIA).
Vassell (SAS) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds. The possession is correctly awarded to the Heat.
